  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u305D\u308C\u306F\u8840\u3068\u306A\u308A\u6BD2\u3068\u306A\u308B",
        "Client": "\u304A\u8179\u304C\u3059\u3044\u305F\u5973\u6027",
        "Description": "\u6728\u306E\u5B9F\u3092\u53D6\u308D\u3046\u3068\u601D\u3063\u3066\u305F\u306E\u306B\u3001\r\n\u30D7\u30B1\u30D7\u30B1\u304C\u5148\u306B\u98DF\u3079\u3061\u3083\u3063\u305F\u306E\u3002\r\n\uFF11\u500B\u3082\u6B8B\u3055\u306A\u3044\u3068\u304B\u3001\u3072\u3069\u3044\u308F\uFF01\r\n\u3053\u306E\u307E\u307E\u3058\u3083\u4ED6\u306E\u98DF\u7CE7\u3082\u5371\u967A\u3088\u3002\r\n\u30CF\u30F3\u30BF\u30FC\u3055\u3093\u3001\u9000\u6CBB\u3057\u3061\u3083\u3063\u3066\u3002\r\n\u98DF\u3079\u7269\u306E\u6068\u307F\u306F\u6016\u3044\u3093\u3060\u304B\u3089\u30FC\uFF01",
        "Target": "\u30D7\u30B1\u30D7\u30B1\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Go Away, Pukei!",
        "Client": "Hungry Woman",
        "Description": "I am absolutely fuming right now!\r\nI spent months, MONTHS, breaking\r\nmy back to have a good harvest this\r\nyear, and it takes only one day for\r\nthat googly-eyed monster to wipe\r\nout all my crops. Think you can\r\ngo harvest its hide for me?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Vade retro, Pukei !",
        "Client": "Femme affam\u00E9e",
        "Description": "Je suis furax ! \u00C7a fait des mois\r\nque je me d\u00E9carcasse pour avoir\r\nune bonne r\u00E9colte cette ann\u00E9e, et\r\nune journ\u00E9e a suffi pour que ce\r\nfichu monstre saccage tout !\r\nTu pourrais le d\u00E9pecer pour moi ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Vattene via, Pukei!",
        "Client": "Donna affamata",
        "Description": "Che rabbia! Ho trascorso mesi,\r\nMESI, a spezzarmi la schiena\r\nper un buon raccolto e quel\r\nmostro dagli occhi spalancati\r\nmi distrugge tutto in un solo\r\ngiorno. Andresti a fargli la\r\npelle per conto mio?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Hau ab, Pukei!",
        "Client": "Hungrige Frau",
        "Description": "Ich koche vor Wut! Ich hab mir \u00FCber\r\nMonate, MONATE den Buckel krumm\r\ngemacht, um dieses Jahr eine gute\r\nErnte zu haben, und in nur einem\r\nTag macht dieses Glubschaugen-\r\nMonster all meine Feldfr\u00FCchte platt.\r\nErntest du seine Haut f\u00FCr mich?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Pukei-Pukei.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Largo, Pukei!",
        "Client": "Mujer hambrienta",
        "Description": "\u00A1Menudo cabreo tengo encima\r\nahora mismo! \u00A1Meses llevo\r\nrompi\u00E9ndome el espinazo para\r\ntener una buena cosecha, y va\r\nese monstruo de ojos saltones\r\ny acaba con ella en un m\u00EDsero\r\nd\u00EDa! \u00BFMe conseguir\u00EDas su piel?",
        "Target": "Caza un Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0423\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438, \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438!",
        "Client": "\u0413\u043E\u043B\u043E\u0434\u043D\u0430\u044F \u0436\u0435\u043D\u0449\u0438\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u042F \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0442\u043E \u0432\u043D\u0435 \u0441\u0435\u0431\u044F! \u042F \u043C\u0435\u0441\u044F\u0446\u0430\u043C\u0438,\r\n\u041C\u0415\u0421\u042F\u0426\u0410\u041C\u0418 \u0433\u043E\u0440\u0431\u0430\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0430\u0441\u044C, \u0447\u0442\u043E\u0431\u044B\r\n\u0441\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044C \u0445\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0448\u0438\u0439 \u0443\u0440\u043E\u0436\u0430\u0439,\r\n\u0430 \u044D\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0443 \u043B\u0443\u043F\u043E\u0433\u043B\u0430\u0437\u043E\u043C\u0443 \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0443\r\n\u0434\u043D\u044F \u0445\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0438\u043B\u043E, \u0447\u0442\u043E\u0431\u044B \u0432\u044B\u0442\u043E\u043F\u0442\u0430\u0442\u044C\r\n\u0432\u0441\u0435 \u043F\u043E\u0441\u0435\u0432\u044B. \u041E\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0448\u044C \u0435\u043C\u0443 \u0437\u0430\r\n\u043C\u043E\u0439 \u0443\u0440\u043E\u0436\u0430\u0439?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438-\u041F\u043E\u043A\u0438",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Id\u017A precz, Pukei!",
        "Client": "G\u0142odna kobieta",
        "Description": "Jestem po prostu w\u015Bciek\u0142a!\r\nSp\u0119dzi\u0142am MIESI\u0104CE, urabiaj\u0105c\r\nsi\u0119 po \u0142okcie, \u017Ceby mie\u0107 dobre\r\nzbiory w tym roku, a ten\r\nwytrzeszcz w jeden dzie\u0144 wszystko\r\nzniszczy\u0142! Skoro nie mam plon\u00F3w,\r\nto chc\u0119 sk\u00F3ry tego potwora!",
        "Target": "Upoluj Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "V\u00E1 embora, Pukei!",
        "Client": "Mulher com fome",
        "Description": "Eu t\u00F4 uma pilha agora! Passei meses,\r\nMESES, trabalhando pesado pra ter\r\numa boa colheita esse ano, e s\u00F3 levou\r\num dia praquele monstro de olhos\r\narregalados destruir toda a minha\r\nplanta\u00E7\u00E3o. Voc\u00EA pode colher o couro\r\ndele pra mim?",
        "Target": "Cace um Pukei-Pukei",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uADF8\uAC83\uC740 \uD53C\uAC00 \uB418\uACE0 \uB3C5\uC774 \uB41C\uB2E4",
        "Client": "\uBC30\uACE0\uD508 \uC5EC\uC131",
